ollateral and executes borrow"],"round":1,"source_agents":["codex_1","opencode_1"]},{"id":"F-003","severity":"Critical","confidence":"high","title":"Cross-chain debt is excluded from accounting due impossible EID condition","locations":["LayerZero/LendStorage.sol:495","LayerZero/LendStorage.sol:497","LayerZero/LendStorage.sol:499","LayerZero/CrossChainRouter.sol:617","LayerZero/CrossChainRouter.sol:227"],"claim":"`LendStorage.borrowWithInterest` only counts `crossChainCollaterals` entries when both `destEid == currentEid` and `srcEid == currentEid`. Real cross-chain entries on destination chain have `srcEid != currentEid`, so they are skipped.","impact":"Borrow checks underestimate existing cross-chain debt (enabling repeated over-borrow), and cross-chain liquidation max-repay can collapse to zero, effectively preventing liquidation.","paths":["_handleBorrowCrossChainRequest -> getHypotheticalAccountLiquidityCollateral -> borrowWithInterest excludes existing cross-chain collateral debt -> new borrow allowed against understated debt","liquidateCrossChain -> getMaxLiquidationRepayAmount(false) -> borrowWithInterest returns 0 -> repayAmount check fails for real liquidations"],"round":1,"source_agents":["codex_1"]},{"id":"F-004","severity":"High","confidence":"high","title":"Source-chain cross-chain debt update drops accrued interest when refreshing borrow index","locations":["LayerZero/CrossChainRouter.sol:710","LayerZero/CrossChainRouter.sol:711","LayerZero/CrossChainRouter.sol:712"],"claim":"When an existing cross-chain borrow is updated in `_handleValidBorrowRequest`, principal is set to `oldPrinciple + payload.amount` and borrowIndex is overwritten with a newer index, without first normalizing old principal to the new index.","impact":"Repeated borrows can under-account true debt versus accrued debt, weakening solvency checks and reducing liquidation effectiveness.","paths":["Existing crossChainBorrows record at old borrowIndex","New ValidBorrowRequest arrives with